These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, british, thai, pakistani
4 different pets are kept: pony, dog, goat, rabbit
1. the owner of the rabbit is not to the right of the owner of the pony##8
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the nigerian##1
3. the british is on the left or right of the thai##3
4. the pakistani is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5
5. the pakistani is not to the left of the owner of the rabbit##8
6. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the british##5
7. the british is somewhere between the nigerian and the owner of the dog##7
8. the british and the owner of the rabbit have the same parity positions##9
9. the thai and the owner of the pony have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | nigerian | british | thai     | pakistani |
| Pet           | goat   | rabbit     | dog | pony  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, lemonade, milk, hot-chocolate
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, singing, board-games, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is video-games and the person drinking lemonade have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's hobby is singing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##8
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is not to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
6. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##5
7. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate     | milk    | fanta | lemonade    |
| Hobby      | cooking | singing | board-games      | video-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, iced-tea, tea, 7up
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, blueberry, pomegranate, watermelon
1. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person eating pomegranate##5
2. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
7. the person eating pineapple is not to the left of the person eating blueberry##8
8. the person drinking iced-tea and the person eating blueberry have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | iced-tea    | tea   | water    | 7up  |
| Food       | blueberry | watermelon | pineapple | pomegranate |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, analyst, mechanic, designer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, blues, pop, salsa
1. the fan d&b is the analyst##1
2. the fan blues is on the right of the fan pop##1
3. the fan blues is somewhere to the left of the analyst##5
4. the fan salsa is on the left or right of the mechanic##3
5. the fan blues is on the left of the librarian##1
6. the designer and the fan salsa have the same parity positions##9
7. the mechanic is on the left or right of the librarian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | designer | mechanic | librarian  | analyst |
| Music-Genre   | pop             | blues          | salsa | d&b    |

