.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, disco, punk, soul
4 different pets are kept: lizard, fish, mouse, bird
1. the fan punk is not the owner of the mouse##6
2. the owner of the lizard and the fan jazz have different parity positions##9
3. the owner of the fish and the fan disco have different parity positions##9
4. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the left of the fan punk##5
5. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the fan soul##1
6. the fan disco is not the owner of the fish##6
7. the fan soul is somewhere to the left of the fan disco##5
8. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the fan jazz##1
9. the owner of the bird is not the fan soul##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | punk | soul  | disco |
| Pet           | fish   | lizard     | mouse | bird      |

