6. the argentine is not to the left of the person watching satire movies##8
7. the australian is somewhere to the left of the person watching satire movies##5
8. the person watching musical movies is not to the right of the australian##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
