2. the owner of the bird is not to the right of the owner of the cat##8
3. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is not the owner of the ferret##6
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
7. the person who's hobby is dancing and the owner of the cat have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
