.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-10::.
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, plum, kale, cucumber
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, quad-bike, scooter, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is not to the left of the person eating cranberry##8
2. the person eating cucumber and the person driving the taxi have the same parity positions##9
3. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
4. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
5. the person eating plum is somewhere between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the taxi##7
6. the person eating cucumber is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | kale | cranberry   | plum | cucumber |
| Transport   | scooter   | quad-bike | subway    | taxi      |

