.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-13::.
There 4 different types of food: potato, pomegranate, zucchini, blueberry
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, thai, brazilian, american
1. the person eating blueberry is not the american##6
2. the american is not to the right of the chinese##8
3. the person eating zucchini is not to the left of the person eating blueberry##8
4. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3
5. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
6. the american is on the far left##1
7. the chinese is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
8. the person eating potato is the thai##1
9. the person eating blueberry and the chinese have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | pomegranate   | blueberry    | zucchini | potato    |
| Nationality   | american | chinese | brazilian   | thai |

