3. the person eating lettuce is somewhere between the fan punk and the fan folk##7
4. the fan folk is somewhere between the fan techno and the person eating lettuce##7
5. the fan r&b is not the person eating spinach##6
6. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
7. the person eating garlic is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | spinach | lettuce | apricot | garlic  |
| Music-Genre   | punk    | r&b | folk | techno |

