2. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
4. the person watching drama movies is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
6. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
7. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
8. the person watching zombie movies and the person drinking hot-chocolate have the same parity positions##9
9. the person watching horror movies and the person drinking lemonade have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | milk   | cola  | lemonade  | hot-chocolate |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | horror | animation | zombie      |

