.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, almond-milk, tea, iced-tea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, reggae, gospel, ambient
 1. the person drinking almond-milk and the fan gospel have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person drinking tea is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
 3. the fan folk is somewhere between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking coffee##7
 4. the fan gospel is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
 5. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan gospel is not to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##8
 7. the person drinking iced-tea and the fan reggae have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the fan ambient##3
 9. the fan ambient is in an odd position##4
10. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the fan folk##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage      | coffee  | iced-tea | tea  | almond-milk |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | gospel     | folk | reggae     |

