.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, hot-chocolate, almond-milk, fanta
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, collecting, dancing, hiking
 1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is not to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##8
 4. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6
 6. the person drinking fanta is not to the right of the person drinking sprite##8
 7. the person drinking fanta and the person who's hobby is collecting have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
 9. the person drinking fanta is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's hobby is collecting have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate    | almond-milk        | fanta   | sprite      |
| Hobby      | hiking | dancing | collecting | rock-climbing |

 